<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:10:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>马尔代夫呼吁印度军队在3月15日前撤军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-calls-withdrawal-indian-troops-by-march-15-2024-01-14/</link><description>总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖去年赢得选举，承诺结束马尔代夫在新德里和北京争夺影响力的地区的“印度优先”政策。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 13:49:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-calls-withdrawal-indian-troops-by-march-15-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士外交官表示，结束乌克兰战争需要俄罗斯的盟友中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/top-diplomats-meet-davos-ukraine-peace-formula-2024-01-14/</link><description>乌克兰在达沃斯世界经济论坛上召开了来自世界各地的国家安全顾问会议，推动其和平方案结束与俄罗斯近两年的战争。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 12:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/top-diplomats-meet-davos-ukraine-peace-formula-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>埃及和中国强调红海航行安全优先-联合声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/egypt-china-stress-priority-safety-security-navigation-red-sea-joint-statement-2024-01-14/</link><description>埃及和中国在周日的联合声明中表示，密切关注红海事态发展，重点关注确保航行安全。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:37:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/egypt-china-stress-priority-safety-security-navigation-red-sea-joint-statement-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>危地马拉阿雷瓦洛即将就任总统，前路艰难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/guatemalas-arevalo-due-assume-presidency-with-difficult-path-ahead-2024-01-14/</link><description>危地马拉当选总统贝尔纳多·阿雷瓦洛将于周日宣誓就职，任期四年，承诺消除根深蒂固的腐败，尽管他将面临分裂的国会和一系列阻止他行使权力的司法尝试。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:03:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/guatemalas-arevalo-due-assume-presidency-with-difficult-path-ahead-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾大选让世界市场松了一口气，但令当地投资者担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-election-relief-world-markets-concern-local-investors-2024-01-14/</link><description>台湾大选可能会缓解全球对台湾与中国关系的担忧，同时引发周一国内股市小幅抛售，因为投资者担心选举结果可能会阻碍经济政策。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 08:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-election-relief-world-markets-concern-local-investors-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交官谴责外国政府就台湾大选后发表的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国外交部和世界各地的大使馆本周末警告各国不要支持台湾民进党（DPP），并谴责祝贺台湾当选总统赖清德的外国政府。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国前官员将访问台湾进行大选后会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-us-officials-visit-taiwan-post-election-talks-2024-01-14/</link><description>美国驻台北事实上的大使馆表示，两名前美国高级官员将于周日抵达台湾进行选举后会谈，并强调美国政府对台海和平的“长期利益”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-us-officials-visit-taiwan-post-election-talks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜外相将访问俄罗斯 - 朝中社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-koreas-foreign-minister-visit-russia-kcna-2024-01-14/</link><description>朝鲜官方通讯社朝中社周日称，朝鲜外交部长崔善姬将于 1 月 15 日至 17 日访问俄罗斯。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-koreas-foreign-minister-visit-russia-kcna-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪与巴西Sigma Lithium就供应协议进行谈判 - FT</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-talks-with-brazils-sigma-lithium-supply-deal-ft-2024-01-14/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周日报道，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪已与巴西西格玛锂业就可能的供应协议、合资或收购进行了谈判。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-talks-with-brazils-sigma-lithium-supply-deal-ft-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新总统面临中国压力，未获得多数席位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</link><description>赖清德虽然以不到一半的选票以微弱优势获胜，但他的政党失去了对议会的控制权，当选总统将不得不依靠议会来通过立法和支出。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜发射导弹，紧张局势升级，部长将访问俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-south-korea-says-2024-01-14/</link><description>最近几周，朝鲜加大了对首尔的压力，宣称其为“主要敌人”，并誓言要增强对美国及其太平洋盟友进行核打击的能力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-south-korea-says-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中方反对日方向台湾当选总统贺电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国驻日本大使馆周日表示，“坚决反对”日本外务大臣上川洋子祝贺台湾新当选总统赖清德的声明。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 04:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新当选总统赖清德将面临中国的愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</link><description>赖在竞选期间多次表示，他希望与中国保持现状，并提出与北京对话。但在北京看来，他是一个分裂主义者，是一个“彻头彻尾的麻烦制造者”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 13:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>西藏不是焦点，镇压持续存在：流亡前领导人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibetan-issues-not-focus-repression-persists-exiled-former-leader-2024-01-13/</link><description>西藏流亡政府前领导人周六表示，国际上对西藏困境的讨论越来越少，但镇压仍在继续，中国正在将其在其他地区的做法应用到其他地区。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibetan-issues-not-focus-repression-persists-exiled-former-leader-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯与中国官员讨论人权、台海问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-raises-human-rights-issues-meeting-with-senior-chinese-official-2024-01-13/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周五在华盛顿会见中国高级官员刘建超时表达了对中国人权问题的担忧，并补充说，他们还讨论了“维护台湾海峡的和平与稳定”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:50:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-raises-human-rights-issues-meeting-with-senior-chinese-official-2024-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>